text:
Phew...
Bottles of alcohol are quite heavy.

I'm sorry, Producer-san...!
I'll carry everything, they're my souvenirs...

After tasting them, they were all exquisite.
It's understandable why you'd want to stock up.

Everyone who always takes care of us...
I want even those who love alcohol to enjoy it.

I understand the feeling of wanting
to share delicious things.

The local liquor store was happy that
you liked the local sake so much.

...Speaking of which, Chiyuki,
Did you not buy any alcohol for yourself?

Actually, just one...
I bought the sake that became my favorite.
